WEBVTT

00:03:29.392 --> 00:03:32.819
Si nje qytetar."

00:03:32.819 --> 00:03:34.415
Keshtu ishte Aron.

00:03:34.415 --> 00:03:39.476
Ai nuk te tregonte. Ai te bente pyetje.

00:03:39.476 --> 00:03:41.226
Por pyetjet e tij flisnin aq qarte

00:03:41.226 --> 00:03:43.914
sa perqafimet e djalit tim kater vjecar.

00:03:43.914 --> 00:03:45.330
Ai po me thoshte,

00:03:45.330 --> 00:03:47.262
"Ti duhet te gjesh nje menyre.

00:03:47.262 --> 00:03:48.938
Ti duhet te gjesh nje ide, sepse atje eshte nje

00:03:48.938 --> 00:03:52.000
e mete ne thelb te sistemit operues

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:53.507
te kesaj demokracie,

00:03:53.507 --> 00:03:57.805
dhe nuk eshte nje e mete 
ne 360 miliard here

00:03:57.805 --> 00:03:59.597
qe demokracia jone perpiqet 
te marre nje vendim.

00:03:59.597 --> 00:04:01.418
Eshte cdo here,